New Zealand Names Team for Season-Opening Rugby Union Test Against Fiji

-- B y   T r a c y   W i t h e r s
-- 
2011-07-19T19:32:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-19/new-zealand-names-team-for-season-opening-rugby-union-test-against-fiji.html
New Zealand rugby union selectors
named the following team for the All Blacks’ season-opening Test
against Fiji on July 22 in Dunedin:  NEW ZEALAND: Wyatt Crockett, Andrew Hore,  Ben Franks ,
Jarrad Hoeata, Ali Williams, Adam Thomson, Richie McCaw
(captain), Liam Messam,  Jimmy Cowan , Colin Slade, Sitiveni
Sivivatu,  Ma’a Nonu ,  Conrad Smith , Zac Guildford,  Mils Muliaina .  Replacements:  Corey Flynn ,  John Afoa , Samuel Whitelock, 
 Jerome Kaino ,  Piri Weepu , Daniel Carter,  Ben Smith .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tracy Withers at 
 twithers@bloomberg.net  